org.xerial.snappy
Class SnappyCodec

java.lang.Object
  org.xerial.snappy.SnappyCodec

public class SnappyCodec
extends Object

Preamble header for SnappyOutputStream.

The magic header is the following 8 bytes data: 

 -126, 'S', 'N', 'A', 'P', 'P', 'Y', 0

Author:
leo
